    "body": "Thanks for summing it up, what about we provide: `[{attributeName, currentRefinement, _clear}]` so that we are in line with the connector API?\n\nAbout the `clear` method, denoting private is already a good move, I wonder if we could go further and not pass it down somehow. But given the current search state internals this might not be feasible.\n",
